# Force LF line endings on text inputs that feed deterministic hashing.
# Without this, Windows checkouts (core.autocrlf=true) convert LF→CRLF in
# `.txt` fixtures, which changes `ingestPaste`'s sha256 and causes
# `result_hash` drift in the cross-OS golden tests.
* text=auto eol=lf
*.docx binary
*.pdf binary
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.woff binary
*.woff2 binary
